  "description": "After too long dealing with other text editors, I\u0026rsquo;m finally returning to Emacs. A critical first step in this is dusting off my old Emacs configuration, which I\u0026rsquo;d named InfoPonEmacs. Since then (2021ce), I\u0026rsquo;ve gotten more particular in my neologisms, specifically about mixing Latin and Greek influences, and have also significantly developed my interest in philosophy, epistemology, etc. (See emsean thought).\nSo, one of the first things I\u0026rsquo;m doing, to more than dust off the system, is renaming it /GnoponEmacs/.\n",
